text: Chris Rorke is an American football coach and former player. He currently serves as the head football coach at Tabor Academy in Marion, Massachusetts. Rorke was the head football coach at Plymouth State University in Plymouth, New Hampshire from 1999 to 2002, compiling a record of 20–21.
